{"tid":644701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【欄后性侵案】最新消息！呂麗瑤前教練被落案控非禮罪","createTime":"2018-04-27T12:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T02:37:03.000Z","uid":78546,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1866886e3d17dfa95d0c21d6be8ad5b562b4aaca","tid":644701,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180427&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58126725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180427%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58126725&d=uqcMyvfCwrYngX29a6QhggRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=cb209508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180427%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58126725&h=3f989fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180427&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58126725</a>"},{"pid":"9b67d9b2d254fc1021b30e79fca3d4438094ef32","tid":644701,"uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"最新消息！警方就去年一名女子指懷疑曾被其教練非禮案件，警方已主動與事主接觸及錄取口供，並於今年1月28日下午拘捕一名77歲本地男子。警方經調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日(27日)控告該名男子一項非禮罪，案件將於5月4日在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n香港田徑隊員、「欄后」呂麗瑤早前於facebook專頁，剖白多年前被教練性侵，事件轟動體壇，更惹起全城關注( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2FnjLL5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FnjLL5&d=uqcMyvfCwrYngX29a6QhggRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4edb4737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FnjLL5</a> )。警方經過約兩個月調查後，於1月採取行動，以涉嫌非禮罪名拘捕1名男子。據悉該被捕男子是一名前田徑教練。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月30日凌晨，呂麗瑤在其23歲生日，於facebook專頁自揭約10年前被中學課外活動的教練性侵犯，對方以按摩為名約到其家中，脫去其牛仔褲及內褲，摸其私處。呂說，公開事件是希望喚起公眾關注兒童性侵犯，鼓勵其他受害人發聲。"},{"pid":"d1b7e9393a6986ffd340698ec1c831763d105e73","tid":644701,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"其實除左摩西仲有咩做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪幫佢驗處"},{"pid":"ef4d55e986b506acac7c48747fe2bdf0ffe38002","tid":644701,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"想知用咩證據告佢"},{"pid":"97436d694bc4afbc0d1ddf8996b0064488dad604","tid":644701,"uid":78546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cCROTUKYCCc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcCROTUKYCCc&d=uqcMyvfCwrYngX29a6QhggRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a77d8e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cCROTUKYCCc</a>"},{"pid":"b093363f1bb2fefc13a1af590004acc8e1031aa4","tid":644701,"uid":144801,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"查完個教練無事嘅<br />\n隻臭雞就風流快活<br />\n個教練就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a1f7d03a933385d9d9f3d098734eddc8a84629","tid":644701,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"過咗咁多年，佢個西都可能有不同男人嘅DNA，點查？"},{"pid":"e9fc8fb9931b3f74118f6c818f0448dfcdaa9e2f","tid":644701,"uid":31,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"光環拎哂 告唔告得入wfc"},{"pid":"3be58cb05fff2c039f5f605716560e6d9b21422a","tid":644701,"uid":3457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b2a1f7d03a933385d9d9f3d098734eddc8a84629","tid":644701,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"過咗咁多年，佢個西都可能有不同男人嘅DNA，點查？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:28:05.000Z","msg":"應該冇屌閪下話😂😂😂😂🤣"},{"pid":"52c2f5cafa249e3ff01e48befacc30abfb0a4c41","tid":644701,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"好想睇下用咩料告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91e833275a19231a67c0f42408d05da38981cb7","tid":644701,"uid":93900,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"等睇連登仔又炒車"},{"pid":"240a5526dde5848f08758562195d4c9be2b11569","tid":644701,"uid":96894,"like":10,